<h2>About This Application</h2>

<p>This is a sample ASP.NET MVC application built with the .NET Framework 4.8.</p>

<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li>ASP.NET MVC 5 architecture</li>
    <li>Razor View Engine</li>
    <li>Model-View-Controller pattern</li>
    <li>Form validation and user interaction</li>
    <li>Responsive CSS styling</li>
    <li>Clean separation of concerns</li>
</ul>

<h3>Technology Stack</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Framework:</strong> .NET Framework 4.8</li>
    <li><strong>Language:</strong> C#</li>
    <li><strong>Web Technology:</strong> ASP.NET MVC 5</li>
    <li><strong>View Engine:</strong> Razor</li>
    <li><strong>Server:</strong> IIS/IIS Express</li>
    <li><strong>UI:</strong> HTML, CSS, Razor Views</li>
</ul>

<h3>Key Benefits of MVC over Web Forms</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Better separation of concerns</li>
    <li>More testable architecture</li>
    <li>Full control over HTML output</li>
    <li>RESTful URL routing</li>
    <li>No ViewState overhead</li>
    <li>Better support for modern web development practices</li>
</ul>
